AnimatedBarChart.tsx: AnimatedBarChart — staggered spring-growth bar chart
AnimatedLineChart.tsx: AnimatedLineChart — SVG line chart with drawing animation
AnimatedPieChart.tsx: AnimatedPieChart — SVG pie with rotational reveal
BenchmarkTable.tsx: BenchmarkTable — tabular benchmark display (MMLU, HumanEval)
ComparisonChart.tsx: ComparisonChart — side-by-side A vs B bars per row
DonutChart.tsx: DonutChart — donut ring with center label + count-up
GrowthCurve.tsx: GrowthCurve — exponential growth curve (compute/params)
HeatmapGrid.tsx: HeatmapGrid — color-coded grid (navy[800] → purple[600])
KPIGrid.tsx: KPIGrid — grid of MetricCards (default 3 columns)
MetricCard.tsx: MetricCard — big animated count-up number + label + delta
PercentageBar.tsx: PercentageBar — horizontal animated percentage bar
RadarChart.tsx: RadarChart — SVG spider/radar chart for model comparison
ScatterPlot.tsx: ScatterPlot — SVG scatter plot with animated reveal
StackedBarChart.tsx: StackedBarChart — stacked segments per group
TimelineChart.tsx: TimelineChart — horizontal timeline with events

@INTERFACES
Bar: { label, value:number, highlight? }
Point: { label, value:number }
Slice: { label, value:number }
RadarAxis: { label, max? }
RadarSeries: { name, values:number[] }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens (seriesColors, colors, fonts, glow, timing) | hooks/interpolateColors | typography/CountUpNumber
external: remotion (interpolate, spring, useCurrentFrame, useVideoConfig)

@STANDARDS
- Series colors: seriesColors[] (purple[600], blue[400], blue[500], purple[700])
- Max 4 series recommended
- All charts animate via timing.reveal (60 frames / 2s)
- Highlighted items get glow.cta
- Czech axis labels default (Čas, Compute, Cena, Výkon)
